WEBVTT

00:00:04.299 --> 00:00:10.300
Everyone wants to be happy, but we all face problems,

00:00:10.300 --> 00:00:12.300
problems that are hard to deal with.

00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:19.820
So, can you ever really be happy?

00:00:19.820 --> 00:00:30.949
At the 2020 Convention of Jehovah's Witnesses,

00:00:30.949 --> 00:00:39.350
you will learn how to find joy even when life is hard,

00:00:39.350 --> 00:00:44.350
and how God has made it possible for us to be happy now and forever.

00:00:44.350 --> 00:00:52.130
Happiness might seem hard to find, but it isn't.

00:00:52.130 --> 00:00:55.130
Come and see for yourself.
